    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104750/extras/640b1b0924b9c2986fd6ad9289e8fdb1.poster.avif?t=1749090227\" width=800 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104750/extras/640b1b0924b9c2986fd6ad9289e8fdb1.webm?t=1749090227\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104750/extras/640b1b0924b9c2986fd6ad9289e8fdb1.mp4?t=1749090227\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>   欢迎来到《密室探险》（EXPEDITION TO THE BACKROOMS），这是一款身临其境的恐怖生存游戏，将带您深入令人不安的无限迷宫 &quot;Backrooms&quot;。这款游戏的灵感来源于流行的网络神话，挑战者要在单调的黄色走廊迷宫中穿行，走廊里充斥着阴森的荧光灯嗡嗡声、令人不安的声音以及对潜伏实体的持续恐惧。你是 Async 公司的勘探队，你来到报告的异常点，寻找异常点，但你会发现什么呢？</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104750/extras/277232f145f8ba340f1f91f23d37d52c.poster.avif?t=1749090227\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104750/extras/277232f145f8ba340f1f91f23d37d52c.webm?t=1749090227\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104750/extras/277232f145f8ba340f1f91f23d37d52c.mp4?t=1749090227\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104750/extras/6f21ccf499c6c31cc04bcd3e4c4521b5.poster.avif?t=1749090227\" width=600 height=58 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104750/extras/6f21ccf499c6c31cc04bcd3e4c4521b5.webm?t=1749090227\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104750/extras/6f21ccf499c6c31cc04bcd3e4c4521b5.mp4?t=1749090227\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>体验 “Backrooms”中令人不寒而栗的氛围，高清画面和环境音效让你紧张不已。</i></strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104750/extras/b7fe99befc5b06d81aa7df90885d85ef.poster.avif?t=1749090227\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104750/extras/b7fe99befc5b06d81aa7df90885d85ef.webm?t=1749090227\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104750/extras/b7fe99befc5b06d81aa7df90885d85ef.mp4?t=1749090227\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104750/extras/bfb28dd89be74fb3302f42c4cd548b4b.poster.avif?t=1749090227\" width=600 height=58 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104750/extras/bfb28dd89be74fb3302f42c4cd548b4b.webm?t=1749090227\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104750/extras/bfb28dd89be74fb3302f42c4cd548b4b.mp4?t=1749090227\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>遇到在密室中游荡的各种实体。有些可能是无害的，有些则是致命的。了解它们的行为，以策略性地避开或对抗它们。</i></strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104750/extras/99ca626515be1edbd0a8d37dd9585a9e.poster.avif?t=1749090227\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104750/extras/99ca626515be1edbd0a8d37dd9585a9e.webm?t=1749090227\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104750/extras/99ca626515be1edbd0a8d37dd9585a9e.mp4?t=1749090227\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104750/extras/3621e1ff8766cde3ab42439e1a11bbe4.poster.avif?t=1749090227\" width=600 height=58 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104750/extras/3621e1ff8766cde3ab42439e1a11bbe4.webm?t=1749090227\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104750/extras/3621e1ff8766cde3ab42439e1a11bbe4.mp4?t=1749090227\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>通过解开错综复杂的谜题和寻找隐藏的线索来揭开密室的秘密，这些线索揭示了这个奇异空间的传说和历史。</i></strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104750/extras/5bbe897078f2aaf30e8d30492a224031.poster.avif?t=1749090227\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104750/extras/5bbe897078f2aaf30e8d30492a224031.webm?t=1749090227\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104750/extras/5bbe897078f2aaf30e8d30492a224031.mp4?t=1749090227\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104750/extras/e3da00719d78bd4173206840c6c2bd9e.poster.avif?t=1749090227\" width=600 height=58 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104750/extras/e3da00719d78bd4173206840c6c2bd9e.webm?t=1749090227\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104750/extras/e3da00719d78bd4173206840c6c2bd9e.mp4?t=1749090227\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>你是一名无畏的探险家，不知何故闯入了 “Backrooms”，这是一个平行空间，里面充满了无穷无尽的房间和走廊，似乎永远也走不完。你必须凭借自己的智慧和所能找到的一切工具，穿越这个噩梦般的迷宫，躲避可怕的实体，找到回到现实世界的方法。</i></strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104750/extras/990c81a919ca126bc965c379b042e10d.poster.avif?t=1749090227\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104750/extras/990c81a919ca126bc965c379b042e10d.webm?t=1749090227\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104750/extras/990c81a919ca126bc965c379b042e10d.mp4?t=1749090227\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104750/extras/caf7257187089e15c4d9e3595876c753.poster.avif?t=1749090227\" width=800 height=76 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104750/extras/caf7257187089e15c4d9e3595876c753.webm?t=1749090227\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104750/extras/caf7257187089e15c4d9e3595876c753.mp4?t=1749090227\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>与周围的动态环境互动，让物体对你的行动做出反应。操纵各种元素来解决谜题、解开秘密，创造出一种身临其境、反应灵敏的游戏体验。</i></strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104750/extras/03fc0b8b846dfb38950ca32ebc5173f6.poster.avif?t=1749090227\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104750/extras/03fc0b8b846dfb38950ca32ebc5173f6.webm?t=1749090227\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104750/extras/03fc0b8b846dfb38950ca32ebc5173f6.mp4?t=1749090227\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>   当你深入 “EXPEDITION TO THE BACKROOMS”时，你会发现奇特的文物，解开具有挑战性的谜题，并拼凑出这个异世界的黑暗历史。但要注意的是：越往深处走，“密室 ”就越危险，越难以预测。你会找到出路，还是会成为另一个迷失的灵魂，永远在无尽的大厅中徘徊？</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>   准备好在 “EXPEDITION TO THE BACKROOMS”中经历一场扣人心弦的冒险吧！在这里，每一步都可能是你的最后一步。你能在疯狂中幸存下来吗？</i></strong></p>",
